ActTelefilm Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of FRANCESCA ACCINELLI of Toronto, Ontario, to be Executive Director of Telefilm Canada, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months or until such time as a new Executive Director is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective September 10, 2022.
